3 (b) ensure the terms and conditions of the new bond are consistent with the original order unless
4 circumstances require adjustment.
5 (4) Courts must notify the surety bail BOND agent, the defendant, and other relevant parties at least
6 30 days before the expiration of the 2-year term to allow sufficient time for renewal or other arrangements. If the
7 court fails to issue a new order or notify the parties within the specified timeframe, the bond must be
